        Constructor for group of simulation experiments.
        Parameters:
        u - Contains experiment means
        var_t - Contains components of variance
        n - Contains experiment size
        rand - Random number generator, no guarantee on current position in sequence
        numTimes - Number of simulation experiments to perform.
        progVal - Shared counter of number of experiments performed across all threads
        filenameTime - Timestamp when this set of experiments was started, to categorize output files
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
